    "It is a \"silver-standard\" dataset.",
    "They deleted the IOB formatting from the IJCNLP 200 NER Corpus in accordance with previous work on the corpus.",
    "It also has mainly three dataset such as IJCNLP 200 NER [10], IJCNLP-2008 [21], [78] and IJCNLP-08 [93].CoNLL 2003 dataset It includes the CoNLL2003 dataset with the piece, pos, and NER labels.",
